15,01'prayer/complaint/driving_lesson'

15,01speed limit 45
15,01and there's dirt under my fingernails
15,01i pick at the one giant scab
15,01that refuses to bleed
15,01a caffeine stain on the dash
15,01soaking up my personal tolerance
15,01for the bitch in front of me
15,01time to slow down
15,01because the spedometer
15,01is my arm
15,01on the ground
15,01like being dragged across water
15,01only not getting wet
15,01scum always floats to the top
15,01as it is in life
15,01it is in heaven
15,01as it will be now and forever

15,01amen

